  "text": "The work in [CITATION_1] deals with the problem of efficient training of convolutional deep belief networks by learning the weights in the frequency domain in order to avoid the time-expensive convolutions. The authors claim about ×8 efficiency on 2D images and ×200 on 3D volumes from medical data.",
